name: Cheesy Cauliflower Tots
author: lamezera
summary: Snack to serve with your favorite dipping sauce.
directions: Preheat the oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C)
Line a baking sheet with parchment paper
Place cauliflower in a large pot and cover with water; bring to a boil
Reduce heat to medium-low and simmer until soft, 5 to 7 minutes
Transfer cauliflower to a food processor
Combine cauliflower crumbs, Cheddar cheese, bread crumbs, and eggs in a large bowl
Shape mixture into 1-inch bites; place on the prepared baking sheet
Bake in the preheated oven until bottoms of tots are golden brown, about 15 minutes
Flip tots over and bake until browned on the opposite sides, about 10 minutes more
